description: This file defines the YangService class which provides various methods to interact with YANG models via API calls, including CRUD operations, parsing, validation, dependency retrieval, comparison, documentation generation, exporting, importing, and version history management.

classes.name: YangService
classes.description: A service class that interfaces with backend API for managing YANG models, offering methods for CRUD operations, parsing, validation, dependency management, comparison, documentation, export/import, and history tracking.

methods.name: getYangModels
methods.description: Fetches a paginated list of YANG models with optional search term.

methods.name: getYangModel
methods.description: Retrieves a specific YANG model by its ID.

methods.name: createYangModel
methods.description: Creates a new YANG model with provided data.

methods.name: updateYangModel
methods.description: Updates an existing YANG model identified by its ID.

methods.name: deleteYangModel
methods.description: Deletes a YANG model by its ID.

methods.name: uploadYangModel
methods.description: Uploads a YANG model file for processing.

methods.name: parseYangModel
methods.description: Parses and validates a string content of a YANG model.

methods.name: validateYangModel
methods.description: Validates a specific YANG model by its ID.

methods.name: getYangModelDependencies
methods.description: Retrieves dependencies for a specific YANG model.

methods.name: getYangModelsByNamespace
methods.description: Fetches YANG models filtered by namespace.

methods.name: getYangModelsByDevice
methods.description: Fetches YANG models associated with a specific device.

methods.name: searchYangModels
methods.description: Performs an advanced search of YANG models with filters.

methods.name: getYangModelTree
methods.description: Retrieves the tree structure of a YANG model for visualization.

methods.name: getYangModelSchema
methods.description: Gets the JSON schema representation of a YANG model.

methods.name: compareYangModels
methods.description: Compares two YANG models and returns their differences.

methods.name: generateDocumentation
methods.description: Generates documentation for a YANG model in specified format.

methods.name: exportYangModel
methods.description: Exports a YANG model in specified format.

methods.name: getYangModelHistory
methods.description: Retrieves version history of a YANG model.
